        GHPREV["gh_preview.sh + lib/gh_preview_warm.sh"]:::sh
        GHACT["gh_action.sh · gh_comment.sh · gh_create.sh (lib/gh_create.py)<br/>gh_picker_palette.sh · gh_row_loader.sh · animated row loaders<br/>gh_batch_worktree.sh (immutable dispatch packet: mode/scope/port/cache-file<br/>so background batches target the initiating popup) · gh_popup.sh · keyhelp.sh"]:::sh
        GHUI["lib/gh_dashboard_ui.py (status header)<br/>gh_palette_verbs.py · gh_patch_picker_cache.py · gh_picker_follow_link.py · gh_palantir_handoff_context.py"]:::py
